Package gw.api.modules.rest.framework.v1.auth.jwt.matchers

Class ClaimMatcher

java.lang.Object
gw.api.modules.rest.framework.v1.auth.jwt.matchers.ClaimMatcher
All Implemented Interfaces:
UserTypeMatcher
Direct Known Subclasses:
ContactAuthorizationIdsMatcher, GwabuidMatcher, PolicyNumbersMatcher, ProducerCodesMatcher
public abstract class ClaimMatcher extends Object implements UserTypeMatcher
Subclass of UserTypeMatcher that matches based on the existence of custom claims on the JWT. By default, this creates an external AuthorizedUser, using the plugin's externalUserPublicid parameter as the underlying internal user.
